  Feasible  production  target 

should  be  given  to  the  farmers  in  the  license  given  to  the  farmers  for  opium 

cultivation  and  the  government  rate  for  the  opium  should  be  given  according  to 

market price in Barabanki. Mentha farmers are having less amount of profit due to 

not getting fair price during the last two years. Government marketing arrangement 

should  be  made  for  it  and  it  should  be  brought  under  crop  insurance  scheme. 

Arrangement of cold storage should be made for the potato storage.  

 

